text: Konarevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Shevchenkovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 94 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Meleuz, 4 km from Antonovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Konarevka
